Package: mariposa
Type: Package
Title: Marburg Initiative for Political and Social Analysis - Statistical Tools for Survey Data
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person("Yannick", "Diehl",
           email = "yannick.diehl@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Professional statistical analysis of survey data with full support
    for survey weights, grouped operations, and tidyverse integration. Provides
    46+ functions for descriptive statistics, hypothesis testing, correlation
    analysis, and post-hoc comparisons. All results are validated against SPSS
    v29 for reproducibility. Designed for survey researchers, social scientists,
    and students working with complex survey designs.
